definitions.definition: A Mexican snack food made of a small tortilla ( soft - or hard - shelled ) filled with ingredients such as meat , rice , beans , cheese , diced vegetables , and salsa .
A yellow stain on a shirt 's armpit caused by sweat or deodorant .
